        <div class="qa-item">
            <h3>Core Problem</h3>
            <p>
                National healthcare systems lack real-time visibility and synchronized control,  
                resulting in delayed, fragmented, and inefficient operational responses.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="qa-item">
            <h3>Architectural Solution</h3>
            <p>
                A sovereign real-time command layer integrating signals from all subsystems  
                and enabling predictive orchestration, automated stabilization,  
                and system-wide operational intelligence.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="qa-item">
            <h3>Impact on Health Systems</h3>
